Detailed Description

An implementation of ASF audio properties.

Member Enumeration Documentation

◆ Codec

enum TagLib::ASF::Properties::Codec

Audio codec types can be used in ASF file.

Enumerator
Unknown 

Couldn't detect the codec.

WMA1 

Windows Media Audio 1

WMA2 

Windows Media Audio 2 or above

WMA9Pro 

Windows Media Audio 9 Professional

◆ length()

virtual TAGLIB_DEPRECATED int TagLib::ASF::Properties::length ( ) const
virtual

Returns the length of the file in seconds. The length is rounded down to the nearest whole second.

Note
This method is just an alias of lengthInSeconds().
Deprecated:
Use lengthInSeconds().
